<s> Doc_891494_0_9_Chemical Doc_891494_10_24_Disease as probable idiosyncratic reaction: case report. </s>
<s> A case of Doc_891494_84_93_Chemical (Doc_891494_95_98_Chemical) Doc_891494_100_114_Disease with increasing Doc_891494_131_139_Disease and EEG and mental changes is described. </s>
